Company Overview of Greenwich Investment Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Greenwich Investment Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations and other businesses. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of United States and Canada. The firm invests in dividend paying stocks of companies. For its fixed income investments, it invests in agency issued bonds. The firm employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolios. It obtains external research to make its investments. Greenwich Investment Management, Inc. wa...
Greenwich Investment Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations and other businesses. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of United States and Canada. The firm invests in dividend paying stocks of companies. For its fixed income investments, it invests in agency issued bonds. The firm employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolios. It obtains external research to make its investments. Greenwich Investment Management, Inc. was founded in November 1999 and is based in Stamford, Connecticut.
