About Us
Our Objective
 

About Us
Personnel at Greenwich Investment Management are seasoned professionals experienced in the management of fixed income and the common stock assets. 
Greenwich Investment Management clients are eleemosynary institutions, taxable individuals, retired persons, financial executives, corporate directors and entrepreneurs.
Client Service
Clients have direct access to our senior management and administrative team.
Full transparency and continuous control of assets
Clients have continuous control of their assets in custody with independent custodians.
Identity of objectives
Employees of Greenwich Investment Management own the same assets that clients own. 








